rving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["If frozen green peas are not available, they can be replaced with tinned green peas, drained: add them at the end of step 2 to the serving bowl with pasta and extra virgin olive oil.","Garnish with chopped parsley, to taste.","Trout can also be replaced with swordfish. Depending on the quality and type of fish, steaming time in <nobr>step 1<\/nobr> can be adjusted to your preference.","If you prefer bigger pieces of fish, don’t add fish to the mixing bowl in <nobr>step 4.<\/nobr> Instead, cut fish in pieces and gently combine in the salad with the spatula.","If you prefer a stronger garlic flavour, rather than removing the garlic clove, chop it <nobr><strong>5 sec\/speed<\/strong><\/nobr> 6 in <nobr>step 3<\/nobr> before sautéing."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}